OL,3,CWildfires in France and Spain force
OL,4,Cmore than 70,000 people to evacuate
OL,6,FWildfires raging in France and Spain
OL,7,Fhave forced mass evacuations and
OL,8,Fprompted both countries to appeal to
OL,9,Ffellow EU members for help.
OL,11,FFrance ordered tens of thousands more
OL,12,Fto leave their homes or holiday
OL,13,Faccommodation on Friday, in areas
OL,14,Fwhich are popular with tourists, after
OL,15,Fwildfires broke out in the south-west
OL,16,Fof the country.
OL,18,FMeanwhile, Spain's government declared
OL,19,Fa national emergency on Friday and
OL,20,Fordered the evacuation of over 10,000
OL,21,Fpeople near Madrid.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
