OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784911676
OL,3,CWildfires in France and Spain force
OL,4,Cmore than 70,000 people to evacuate
OL,6,FBoth nations have been battling with
OL,7,Fextraordinarily high temperatures and
OL,8,Fdry weather in recent months, making
OL,9,Fthem exceptionally prone to wildfires.
OL,11,FIn southwestern France on Friday, the
OL,12,Fgovernment ordered more mass
OL,13,Fevacuations on the Atlantic coast. An
OL,14,Festimated 40,000 people have been
OL,15,Fdriven from their homes over the past
OL,16,Ftwo days in the region.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
