OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784911676
OL,3,CWildfires in France and Spain force
OL,4,Cmore than 70,000 people to evacuate
OL,6,FMore than 100 square kilometres have
OL,7,Falready been burned by the blaze,
OL,8,Fwhich has been raging since Wednesday
OL,9,Fnear the Cap Ferret peninsula, which
OL,10,Fis popular with tourists. Some people
OL,11,Fwere forced to flee by boat.
OL,13,FThe fires began on Tuesday in the
OL,14,Fsmall commune of Saumos, near Bordeaux.
OL,16,FFrance requested the activation of the
OL,17,FEuropean Union's Civil Protection
OL,18,FMechanism.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
