OL,3,CWildfires in France and Spain force
OL,4,Cmore than 70,000 people to evacuate
OL,6,F"We will soon be able to rely on
OL,7,Freinforcements including two Croatian
OL,8,FCanadair firefighting aircraft, two
OL,9,FPortuguese Air Tractor aircraft, and
OL,10,Ftwo heavy-lift Black Hawk helicopters
OL,11,Ffrom the Czech Republic and Slovakia,"
OL,12,FFrench President Emmanuel Macron said.
OL,14,FSpanish Interior Minister Fernando
OL,15,FGrande-Marlaska said that Italy and
OL,16,FGreece are each sending two Canadair
OL,17,Fwater-dumping planes.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@fO]
