OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784911676
OL,3,CWildfires in France and Spain force
OL,4,Cmore than 70,000 people to evacuate
OL,6,F"We are experiencing a dramatic
OL,7,Fsituation, not just in several Spanish
OL,8,Fregions but also in neighbouring
OL,9,Fcountries," Spanish Prime Minister
OL,10,FPedro Sanchez wrote on X.
OL,12,F"My solidarity with all the people who
OL,13,Fhave been affected and been forced to
OL,14,Fleave their homes."
