PN,30307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784911676
OL,3,CWildfires in France and Spain force
OL,4,Cmore than 70,000 people to evacuate
OL,6,FSpain has seen an estimated 500 square
OL,7,Fmiles already burned this year, over
OL,8,Ffour times the amount of terrain that
OL,9,Fwas burned through the first half of
OL,10,F2025.
OL,12,FThis year's fires include Spain's
OL,13,Fsecond-largest ever fire that consumed
OL,14,Fsome 120 square miles in recent days
OL,15,Fin the province of Guadalajara north
OL,16,Fof Madrid.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
