PN,30308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784911676
OL,3,CWildfires in France and Spain force
OL,4,Cmore than 70,000 people to evacuate
OL,6,FThirteen people, including several
OL,7,FBritish nationals, were also killed in
OL,8,Fa fire in southern Spain earlier this
OL,9,Fmonth, the deadliest fire in recent
OL,10,Fmemory for Spain.
OL,12,FSpain has called for a pact between
OL,13,Fpolitical parties to fight climate
OL,14,Fchange. Temperatures are expected to
OL,15,Ftop 39C in parts of southeastern Spain
OL,16,Fin the coming days, including a high
OL,17,Fof 44C.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
