OL,3,CWildfires in France and Spain force
OL,4,Cmore than 70,000 people to evacuate
OL,6,FSouthern Europe has seen multiple
OL,7,Flarge fires this summer. Europe is the
OL,8,Fworld's fastest-warming continent,
OL,9,Fwith temperatures increasing twice as
OL,10,Fquickly as the global average since
OL,11,Fthe 1980s, according to the European
OL,12,FUnion's Copernicus Climate Change
OL,13,FService.
OL,15,FGlobally, 2025 was the third-hottest
OL,16,Fyear on record, bringing severe heat
OL,17,Fwaves across Europe.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
