OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784911676
OL,3,CWildfires in France and Spain force
OL,4,Cmore than 70,000 people to evacuate
OL,6,FScientists warn that climate change is
OL,7,Fexacerbating the frequency and
OL,8,Fintensity of heat and dryness,
OL,9,Fespecially in southeastern Europe,
OL,10,Fmaking the region more vulnerable to
OL,11,Fhealth impacts and wildfires.
